name: Breast Cancer: Neoadjuvant Chemotherapy with Surgery
description: Pathway for the Early Stage HER2+ Breast Cancer Pathway for neoadjuvant chemotherapy with surgery.

preconditions.cql: exists("Primary Cancer Condition" PrimaryCancer where PrimaryCancer.code.text.value ~ 'Malignant neoplasm of breast (disorder)')
exists([Observation: "HER2 [Presence] in Breast cancer specimen by Immune stain"] Her2 where Her2.value.text.value ~ 'Positive')

condition.cql: exists([Observation: "Primary tumor.clinical [Class] Cancer code"] TLarge where ToConcept(TLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "T3 category (finding)" or ToConcept(TLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "T4 category (finding)")

exists([Observation: "Primary tumor.clinical [Class] Cancer code"] TLarge where ToConcept(TLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "T3 category (finding)" or ToConcept(TLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "T4 category (finding)")

exists([Observation: "Primary tumor.clinical [Class] Cancer code"] TLarge where ToConcept(TLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "T3 category (finding)" or ToConcept(TLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "T4 category (finding)")

exists([Observation: "Primary tumor.clinical [Class] Cancer code"] TSmall where ToConcept(TSmall.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "T0 category (finding)" or ToConcept(TSmall.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "T1 category (finding)" or ToConcept(TSmall.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "T2 category (finding)")

exists([Observation: "Regional lymph nodes.clinical [Class] Cancer code"] NLarge where ToConcept(NLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "N1 category (finding)" or ToConcept(NLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "N2 category (finding)" or ToConcept(NLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "N3 category (finding)")

exists([Observation: "Regional lymph nodes.clinical [Class] Cancer code"] NLarge where ToConcept(NLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "N1 category (finding)" or ToConcept(NLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "N2 category (finding)" or ToConcept(NLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "N3 category (finding)")

exists([Observation: "Regional lymph nodes.clinical [Class] Cancer code"] NLarge where ToConcept(NLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "N1 category (finding)" or ToConcept(NLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "N2 category (finding)" or ToConcept(NLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "N3 category (finding)")
exists([Observation: "Regional lymph nodes.clinical [Class] Cancer code"] N0 where ToConcept(N0.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "N0 category (finding)")

Surgery1.label: Surgery
Surgery1.cql: exists([Procedure: "Lumpectomy of breast (procedure) code"]) or exists([ServiceRequest: "Lumpectomy of breast (procedure) code"])

ChemotherapyTCHP.label: Chemotherapy TCHP
ChemotherapyTCHP.cql: exists([MedicationRequest: "10 ML Doxorubicin Hydrochloride 2 MG/ML Injection code"] MR where ToConcept(MR.medication as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "10 ML Doxorubicin Hydrochloride 2 MG/ML Injection")

ChemotherapyACTHP.label: Chemotherapy ACTHP
ChemotherapyACTHP.cql: exists([MedicationRequest: "Cyclophosphamide 1000 MG Injection code"] MR where ToConcept(MR.medication as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "Cyclophosphamide 1000 MG Injection")

ChemotherapyddACTHP.label: Chemotherapy ddACTHP
ChemotherapyddACTHP.cql: exists([MedicationRequest: "14 ML pertuzumab 30 MG/ML Injection code"] MR where ToConcept(MR.medication as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "14 ML pertuzumab 30 MG/ML Injection")

Surgery2.label: Surgery
Surgery2.cql: exists([Procedure: "Lumpectomy of breast (procedure) code"]) or exists([ServiceRequest: "Lumpectomy of breast (procedure) code"])

condition.cql: exists([Observation "Pathologic response code"] Response where ToConcept(Response.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "Complete")

exists([Observation "Pathologic response code"] Response where ToConcept(Response.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "Partial" or ToConcept(Response.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "Stable" or ToConcept(Response.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "Progressive")
exists([Observation: "Regional lymph nodes.clinical [Class] Cancer code"] N0 where ToConcept(N0.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "N0 category (finding)")

exists([Observation: "Regional lymph nodes.clinical [Class] Cancer code"] NLarge where ToConcept(NLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "N1 category (finding)" or ToConcept(NLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "N2 category (finding)" or ToConcept(NLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "N3 category (finding)")
